<p><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFLudlow2000">Ludlow, Morwenna (2000). <i><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=U32mir3alW8C&amp;printsec=frontcover" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=U32mir3alW8C&amp;printsec=frontcover" rel="nofollow">Universal Salvation: Eschatology in the Thought of Gregory of Nyssa and Karl Rahner</a></i>. <a href="/wiki/Oxford_University_Press" title="Oxford University Press">Oxford University Press</a>. pp.&#160;2–3. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0198270224" class="internal">ISBN 0198270224</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=U32mir3alW8C&amp;printsec=frontcover" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=U32mir3alW8C&amp;printsec=frontcover" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=U32mir3alW8C&amp;printsec=frontcover</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-08-09</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Universal+Salvation%3A+Eschatology+in+the+Thought+of+Gregory+of+Nyssa+and+Karl+Rahner&amp;rft.aulast=Ludlow&amp;rft.aufirst=Morwenna&amp;rft.au=Ludlow%2C+Morwenna&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B2%E2%80%933&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BOxford+University+Press%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=0198270224&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DU32mir3alW8C%26printsec%3Dfrontcover&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Universal_reconciliation"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></p>
